item.title: About
item.description: Collin Dougherty is a driven leader, problem solver, and researcher with a strong focus on efficiency. Pursuing a Master’s in Mathematics and Data Science, and holding degrees in Psychology and Mathematics, Collin has a unique skill set to tackle complex data science problems. He has experience in cancer research, sports analytics, and data analysis across multiple industries. Collin understands the importance of making data easy to interact with, and enjoys working with clients to deliver meaningful insights from complex data.
